'''Tito Rutaremara''' (wavutse mu 1944) ni [[umunyarwanda]] w'[[umunyapolitiki]].

== Amateka ==

=== Amashuri yize ===
'''Tito Rutaremara''' yize amashuri abanza n'ayisumbuye mu [[Rwanda]], yiga ikiciro cya kabiri cya Kaminuza mu gihugu cya [[Ubugande|Uganda]]. Rutaremara afite impamyabumenyi y'ikirenga mu ubumenyi bw'isi, ndetse ni mpamyabumenyi ihanitse mu bijyanye no gutegura imijyi n'ibyaro yakuye mu gihugu cy'[[Ubufaransa]] <ref name=":0">https://www.parliament.gov.rw/index.php?id=135&width=650&detailId=138</ref><ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/section/read/35731</ref>.

=== Imirimo yakoze ===
'''Tito Rutaremara''' yabaye umunyabanga wa Rwandase Patriotic Front (RPF) kuva mu mwaka wa 1987 kugera 1993. Kuva kandi mu 1994 kugera 2000 yari mubari bagize inteko y'inzibacyuho. Rutarema kandi yanayoboye komisiyo yari ishinzwe itegeko nshinga n'andi mategeko kuva mu mwaka wa 2000 kugera mu 2003. Kuva mu 2003 kugera mu 2011, Rutaremara yabaye umuvunyi mukuru<ref name=":0" />. Nyakubahwa Perezida wa Rebulika y'u [[Rwanda]] yashyize '''Tito Rutaremara'''  mu ntekishingamategeko umutwe wa sena mu Ukwakira 2011<ref>https://www.acauthorities.org/news/drtito-rutaremara-appointed-senator</ref>. Kuva mu mwaka 2019 Rutaremara ni umuyobozi w'inama ngishwanama y'inararibonye aho yasimbuye [[Iyamuremye Augustin]]<ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/news/kagame-names-new-cabinet-ministers</ref>.

